Cortex provides repository scanning, governance checks, and AI context generation tools.

Usage:
  cortex [command]

Available Commands:
  commit      Generate commit health report
  commit      Generate commit discipline suggestions
  completion  Generate the autocompletion script for the specified shell
  context     AI context pipeline commands
  feature     Generate feature traceability report
  gov         Governance checks for Cortex
  help        Help about any command
  status      Show Cortex project status and roadmap analysis
  version     Print the version number of Cortex
  xray        Run XRAY scan

Flags:
  -h, --help      help for cortex
  -v, --verbose   enable verbose output

Use "cortex [command] --help" for more information about a command.
